learn.</strong>For further help and instructions on flying a drone, try online resources on YouTube or other sites that walk you through the process and offer more tips.</li>\n</ol>', 'Training', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '88-autosave-v1', '', '', '2014-12-05 16:26:27', '2014-12-05 21:26:27', '', 88, 'http://localhost/TheDroneStore/88-autosave-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
