pulated and built-up areas, lack of any UAS training or aviation experience, flying larger UAS (&gt;25 kg), or flying beyond visual line of sight. UAS operators should consider these risks before submitting an SFOC application.</p>', 'SFOC', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '92-revision-v1', '', '', '2014-12-05 16:50:13', '2014-12-05 21:50:13', '', 92, 'http://localhost/TheDroneStore/92-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
